{"tid":195914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(有片)日本薯仔失收 供港卡樂B薯片要停售？","createTime":"2017-04-11T02:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T07:50:22.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"92a1125acd4142f6c1a4fbf90e484b976319cb67","tid":195914,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1765000/1767745/calbee_thumb_20170410_C_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1765000%2F1767745%2Fcalbee_thumb_20170410_C_1024.jpg&h=b41feca3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本北海道去年打破9年來沒有颱風的紀錄，連續受多個颱風吹襲致馬鈴薯嚴重失收。日本卡樂B宣佈部份薯片商品4月起暫時停賣，包括香港有售的「淡鹽味」及「幸福牛油味」薯片等逾15種口味產品，或會出現斷貨。卡樂B在港設有廠房，港產卡樂B薯片不受日本失收影響，因其原料由其他地方進口。不過，一些直接由日本入口卡樂B薯片的超市就受到影響。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170411/large/1491876189_cb49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170411%2Flarge%2F1491876189_cb49.jpg&h=d05ff6b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據日本傳媒報道，去年8月尾北海道颱風影響當地馬鈴薯收成，惟日產卡樂B有7成原料來自北海道，現在薯仔存貨已見底，卡樂B需暫停出售部份產品，未有預計何時可恢復供應。記者昨到零食專賣店「優品360」了解，見店內仍有售日本進口薯片，包括「堅燒麻油梅味」和期間限定的「明太子牛油」等口味。<br />\n一田百貨發言人指，旗下的卡樂B薯片大部份都是日本進口貨，去年底來貨開始緊張，尤其是期間限定或特別口味的薯片，但至今未有收到供應商指停止供應，超市現時仍有售，會因應情況會增加歐洲進口的薯片來貨。<br />\nCity&rsquo;super回應傳媒查詢時指，預料卡樂B供應未來2至3個月會出現短缺，惟現時供應未有受影響。  <br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1765000/1767745/15b92a7f-e67f-461f-b598-73868dda5eb3_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1765000%2F1767745%2F15b92a7f-e67f-461f-b598-73868dda5eb3_1024.jpg&h=2df982d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">北角有入口零食店有售4款口味的日版薯片，店員稱其中3款售完便無貨。(龐浩吉攝)</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170411/56548313\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170411%2F56548313&d=4DrNtUYtvprXc3sGeUgfz%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=fbcbe258\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170411%2F56548313&h=149fc71a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170411/56548313</a>"},{"pid":"980f09e57c848e079396e11bed03b8716010f251","tid":195914,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:51:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc179909f53c4d5916a31745ba5cccb698c1d1cd","tid":195914,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff7d1e217915882f5cf7cecdd15e1213481425d","tid":195914,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T03:02:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eff96dcb8cca5bca67c0cb8e854b53b561e38c8","tid":195914,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T03:08:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d611f575e286601cf838a4b4c2af39ca10f342a","tid":195914,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T03:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e1edad34e454ee517f8c189e1d3a9738fcaf56","tid":195914,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T04:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e8d7ea32d6555d9fc4de79465da07a9e95ab41","tid":195914,"uid":16380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T04:35:07.000Z","msg":"原來d 薯片真係有落薯仔整<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140bc71da8089da8d027e59f69ef4f50f0e9d